486
00:51:56,400 --> 00:52:00,340
Kdekoľvek s tebou idem, vždy je to
miesto, ktoré má rada Ha Na.

487
00:52:01,400 --> 00:52:03,480
Naozaj?

488
00:52:04,920 --> 00:52:09,119
